---
title: Japanese Hoisin Miso–Glazed Trout with Cucumber Carrot Salad
description: Flavors of hoisin—a sweet and tangy Cantonese-style sauce—and miso elevate flaky trout and warm rice in this restaurant-style dish. After topping the fish with savory hoisin miso glaze, you'll simply pop it in the oven to roast. While the fish cooks, you'll whip up a refreshing sesame carrot and cucumber salad to serve on the side.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/661d65723d20ae432f30b536-8a7a3bfb.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/67c58df4f0a31bc0c3010be0-en-US.pdf
nutrition:
  calories: 780 kcal
  fat: 38 g
  saturated fat: 9 g
  carbohydrates: 75 g
  sugar: 26 g
  protein: 31 g
  fiber: 2 g
  sodium: 1100 mg
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/japanese-hoisin-miso-glazed-trout-67c58df4f0a31bc0c3010be0
author: HelloFresh
cuisine: East Asia
course: main course
servings: 2
time required: 45 minutes
---

Adjust rack to top position and preheat oven to 425 degrees.

In a #small pot{}, combine @jasmine rice{1/2%cup}, 3/4 cups @water{3/4%cups}, and a @salt{pinch}. Bring to a boil, then cover and reduce to a low simmer. Cook until rice is tender, ~{15-18%minutes}.

Keep covered off heat until ready to serve.

Meanwhile, wash and dry produce.

Trim and quarter @mini cucumber{2} lengthwise; slice crosswise into 1/2-inch-thick quarter-moons. Trim and thinly slice @scallions{2}, separating whites from greens.

In a #medium bowl{}, combine cucumbers, scallion whites, @shredded carrots{4%oz}, @sesame dressing{1.5%oz}, @white wine vinegar{1%tsp}, and @sugar{1/4%tsp}. Season generously with @salt{} and @pepper{}.

In a #small bowl{}, combine @hoisin sauce{2%tbsp}, @miso sauce concentrate{1}, and @umami ginger sauce{4%tbsp}; set aside.

Pat @steelhead trout{10%oz} dry with #paper towels{}; season all over with @salt{} and @pepper{}.

Place trout, skin sides down, on a #baking sheet{}. Evenly spread tops of trout with hoisin miso glaze. Roast on top rack until trout is cooked through, ~{10-12%minutes}.

Fluff rice with a #fork{}.

Divide rice, trout, and cucumber carrot salad between plates. Sprinkle everything with scallion greens and serve.

> Fish is fully cooked when internal temperature reaches 145°.